config.nbtvoid.title: Configure NBT Void
config.nbtvoid.isEnabledDescription: If disabled, void will not save any items
config.nbtvoid.reducedSourcesDescription: Only check items in inventories and equipment
config.nbtvoid.maxDisplayItemsDescriptio: Maximum amount of rows (9 items) void tab will display
config.nbtvoid.maxStoredItemsDescription: Maximum amount of rows (9 items) void will store
config.nbtvoid.defaultSearchQueryDescrip: Default search query in the void tab
config.nbtvoid.nameCheckDescription: Search type for occurrence of name queries
config.nbtvoid.nbtCheckDescription: Search type for occurrence of NBT queries
config.nbtvoid.ignoreNbtDescription: NBTs that will be ignored when checking does item have NBT
config.nbtvoid.removeNbtDescription: NBTs that will be removed when adding to void
config.nbtvoid.doDynamicUpdateDescriptio: Update void after saving to match current configuration
config.nbtvoid.doAsyncSearchDescription: Do searching in separate thread to avoid lag if you have a lot of items (/!\ May crash your game)
config.nbtvoid.clearVoidDescription: Clear NBT void, similiar to the "Clear Void" keybind
config.nbtvoid.updateExceptionsDescripti: Update the void to match current exceptions, similiar to the "Dynamic Update" config (don't forget to save changes in "Ignore" and "Remove" NBTs in order for it to work)
config.nbtvoid.loadVoidDescription: Load void from the file, similiar to the "Load Void" keybind
config.nbtvoid.saveVoidDescription: Save void to the file, similiar to the "Save Void" keybind
status.nbtvoid.updating: NBT void is currently updating, please wait...
